    "It must be integrated into causal models to accurately reflect the biological response to external stimuli within the spatial and temporal scale of interest and to generate causal hypotheses 124.",
    "In the broader context of precision medicine, integrating digital twins that reflect these multiscale, multiomics and adaptive features poses even more challenges.",
